{"title":"六月的乡村","authors":["高风"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月的乡村\t高风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月里，淡绿的枣花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘散点点清香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殷红的石榴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃起团团火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南风鼓动着风箱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳像一炉红炭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才几日工夫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把田野锻得金黄耀眼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄醒得好早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朦胧里人声语喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵马，套车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修仓，磨镰，……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲催着脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步摇落热汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀的沙沙声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与心中的歌儿一般甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里，麦把待运，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场上，石磙叫唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大车咕咚咚来回穿梭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶车人扬着鞭嫌慢。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月的清晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月的新农村呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在社会主义大道上飞速向前！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}